query: INSERT INTO Item (_id, item_name, short_name, avg_24h_price, base_price, change_last_48h_percent, width, height, wiki, item_types) SELECT * FROM UNNEST($1::text[], $2::text[], $3::text[], $4::int[], $5::int[], $6::real[], $7::int[], $8::int[], $9::text[], $10::text[]) ON CONFLICT(_id) DO UPDATE SET avg_24h_price = EXCLUDED.avg_24h_price, change_last_48h_percent = EXCLUDED.change_last_48h_percent;
